      "text": "Just returned from a weeks stay with my husband and 2 teenage sons. This hotel is faultless. Room was amazing and clean with a great view. Great location near train stop. You are one stop away from the Burj/Dubai Mall.  Pool staff can’t do enough to help you! Life guards are constantly ensuring everyone is safe, safety really is the priority with children in the pool. Reassuring to see! Staff up there find you somewhere to sit, get you towels etc.  Breakfast was busy but tasty! Room service lady was brilliant and went the extra mile every morning! Free Shuttle bus to the mall and beach was a great added touch! Very handy! All in all the staff make this hotel! Incredible!\nThank you for a fantastic holiday. We can’t wait to come back to the Towers Rotana!",
      "title": "Amazing!!!",
