      "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g295424-d306762-r945687797-Reviews-Towers_Rotana-Dubai_Emirate_of_Dubai.html?m=66827#review945687797",
      "text": "Excellent city hotel in the heart of Dubai.\nThe location is superb - 3 minutes to the metro station, about 25 minutes walk to Burj Khalifa, 15 minutes by taxi to La Mer beach.\n\nI had a club room on the 22nd floor with a gorgeous view, the room is clean and spacious, has everything you need including a capsule coffee machine.\n\nThere is a free shuttle to La Mer beach 4 times a day, you get a beach bag and towel. The hotel has a pool, it is on the 6th floor overlooking the Dubai high-rises. \n\nThe hotel has several restaurants, with different types of food, buffet and order a la carte. European and Asian cuisine, all very tasty and fresh. HB+ meals include wine and beer, you can choose lunch or dinner.\n\nOn the first floor is a traditional English pub with live music, highly recommended.\n\nI would like to mention the very friendly and always ready to help hotel staff, especially the reception staff: Shokhista, Prashant and Daryl, all speak excellent English and Shokhista knows Russian.  \n\nIt's hard to pick on anything, everything is to a very high standard, maybe we should add usb or type-c sockets to the room.\nI definitely recommend the hotel - perfect combination of price/quality!",
      "title": "Comfortable vacation in Dubai",
      "trip_type": "Solo travel",
      "travel_date": "2024-03-31",
